Package: RegCompassR
Title: Multiome-Supported Reaction Capacity and GRN Meta-Module Analysis
Version: 1.2.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "RegCompass", family = "Developers", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "dev@example.com"))
Description: Provides a formal multiome workflow for sample-aware SuperCell RNA+ATAC metacells, metacell fragment aggregation, cell-type-stratified metabolic peak-gene relinking, RNA-GPR reaction capacity, ATAC-supported reaction confidence, sample-specific Pando gene-regulatory networks, GRN-defined reaction meta-modules, and cached microCOMPASS scoring.
